ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Employment and Social Development of DANA ADES-LANDY, of Montréal, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of four years, effective January 30, 2018.
